  "further_info": "The module serves as the foundational element for subsequent modules within the Entrepreneurial Skills Certificate (Entrepreneurial Skills Program). To receive ECTS points, students are required to maintain a minimum attendance rate of 80%, participate in a final presentation, and thoroughly document their learning experiences in a learning diary. This module is highly recommended for students pursuing a Bachelor's, Master's, or Doctoral degree, as well as postdoctoral researchers.",
